summary: It’s only a matter of time before I break
title: It’s only a matter of time before I break
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2NTn7ht

by Poncho_muskrat

They sat in silence for a few minutes, enjoying the peace, until Peter broke it.

“Have you ever thought about flying really high and just falling?” Peter asked quietly. Tony seemed confused by the question.

“Care to elaborate?”

“Not using your superpowers to save you, and just dropping?”

“…..that’s suicide, kid.” Tony said like he was talking to a five year old.

“I know.”

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Peter has a hard time coping with the weight of the world on his shoulders

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

summary: Can you elaborate on the Nat and Tony one? I’d like to see them interact if that’s okay?
question: Can you elaborate on the Nat and Tony one? I’d like to see them interact if that’s okay?
answer:
The original drabble is here.  (Tony is the only one awake when Nat’s hit with the stomach flu.)

_____

Tony slaps the wall when he steps off the elevator.  The machines in the facility are modern and silent, and everyone knows it’s bad news to sneak up on an assassin, even when she’s preoccupied.

True to Tony’s expectations, Nat whirls around, dragging one hand across her lips and balling the other into a fist, ready to fight.  Her reflexes haven’t slowed a lick.  Tony’s spent time wondering how much is training and how much is instinct.  He ponders the question again as recognition flashes in Nat’s eyes and her body seems to think it’s safe to start gagging again.

“Stark,” Nat coughs into the depths of the sink.  “What the fuck?”

“I don’t know.”  Tony shrugs even though she can’t see him.  “What the fuck’s up with you?”

Nat spits.  “Nothing.  I’m fine.”  The hand that’s not clutching the counter is back down by her side, but her walls are up.

“Yeah, you look totally fine.”  Tony rolls his eyes.  “We have pepto, you know.  Just got a delivery of groceries and stuff.”

“Whatever.”  Nat’s shoulders twitch as she tries to stifle another heave.

“Vodka, too,” Tony offers.  “If you just want to, you know.  Get it up faster.”

“I’ll just—”  Nat’s breath hitches.  “Ride it out in my room.”  She presses her lips together and brushes past Tony.

“Hey, at least run the disposal.”  Tony makes a face at the back of her head.

“Oh, fuck you.”  Nat’s arm snakes protectively around her stomach as she bypasses the elevator and stomps toward the stairs.  The heavy fire door slams behind her.

“Yeah,” Tony mutters.  He flips on the faucet with one finger, then presses the button to initiate the roar of the garbage disposal.  “Yeah.  Fuck me.”

summary: @imissleeandluke Here is your ship darling! I am so sorry you waited so long! Enjoy!!! I ship you with... Sam Wilson!!! How did...
body:
@imissleeandluke Here is your ship darling! I am so sorry you waited so long! Enjoy!!!

I ship you with…

Sam Wilson!!!

How did you met:

You were taking out your dog for a walk around the city but also you wanted go out and meet some new dogs and hopefully see one of your friends. While walking your dog noticed something very interesting and suddenly he started running before you could grip his leash tighter and hold him back. Your dog didn’t return despite your calls and your tries to catch him. You tried to reach him but he was so fast and you lost him out of your sight in few seconds. You became very sad and angry at the same time but you had to find your dog. Walking around the place you asked few people if they have seen your dog but their answer was always negative, you shouted his name couple of times but still nothing. It was already dark so you decided to rest for a while and continue your search later. You sat on a bench and covered your face with your hands focusing on how to find your dog quickly.

“You are such a good boy come on!” you heard someone say behind you and you quickly turned around. You were happy to see that someone has found your dog.

“I think it belongs to you miss” the tall man said with a half grin on his face.

“Yes! Yes he is mine! Thank you so much!” you stood up from the bench and walked over to pet and hug your dog. “You were such a bad boy!” you said as you gently petted your seemingly very happy dog!

“Yes he was very bad, but luckily he is returned!” he said and gently pet his head. He noticed your tears from before and instantly frowned.

“Is everything alright?” he asked his tone changing from relaxed to worry.

“Yes it is, it was just a very stressful day.” You answered honestly and wiped them off your cheek.

First date:

For the first date he decided to take you out in your favorite restaurant. He already knew what your favorite restaurant is and he was very happy when he found out it was not one of that glamorous places where people wear fancy but uncomfortable clothes. The restaurant was very cozy and everything inside was designed to make people feel even better. When you two arrived the waiter showed you your table and when you sat down and chose your meals he left. Sam’s mood was like usual which means you were laughing most of the time. You noticed that he is a very nice guy and that you two have a lot of things in common. You two have a very good time together and at the end of your date you were already looking forward to your next meeting.

Relationship:

Your relationship is kind of that relationship in which one partner always teases the other one about the littlest things just to see them get fierce and pouty. In this case Sam always finds something to tease you about because he finds you adorable when you get angry and try to ignore him. He would then wrap arms around you and kiss your cheek couple of times until you start talking with him again. He knows how to fight and he is very good doing it so he is willing to teach you couple of moves and help you improve your skills. Sam may seem as very funny and sometimes serious person but he has a very sweet and gentle side whenever he is with you. He often kisses your hand, cheek and forehead and gives you weirdest but still the cutest nicknames and it’s one of his ways to show how much he loves you and how much you mean to him. He likes to listen to you while you sing or play the piano, he finds your voice beautiful and he has so many videos in his phone of you singing or playing the piano.

Nicknames:

Dearest, lady, bug…- He has so many nicknames for you and always keeps adding new ones on the list

Luv, ass- First one when he surprises you or when he is gentle and the second one when he teases you about something

                                   //Gifs I used don’t belong to me//

Luv, ass- First one when he surprises you or when he is gentle and the second one when he teases you about something

trail.content:
@imissleeandluke Here is your ship darling! I am so sorry you waited so long! Enjoy!!!

I ship you with…

Sam Wilson!!!

How did you met:

You were taking out your dog for a walk around the city but also you wanted go out and meet some new dogs and hopefully see one of your friends. While walking your dog noticed something very interesting and suddenly he started running before you could grip his leash tighter and hold him back. Your dog didn’t return despite your calls and your tries to catch him. You tried to reach him but he was so fast and you lost him out of your sight in few seconds. You became very sad and angry at the same time but you had to find your dog. Walking around the place you asked few people if they have seen your dog but their answer was always negative, you shouted his name couple of times but still nothing. It was already dark so you decided to rest for a while and continue your search later. You sat on a bench and covered your face with your hands focusing on how to find your dog quickly.

“You are such a good boy come on!” you heard someone say behind you and you quickly turned around. You were happy to see that someone has found your dog.

“I think it belongs to you miss” the tall man said with a half grin on his face.

“Yes! Yes he is mine! Thank you so much!” you stood up from the bench and walked over to pet and hug your dog. “You were such a bad boy!” you said as you gently petted your seemingly very happy dog!

“Yes he was very bad, but luckily he is returned!” he said and gently pet his head. He noticed your tears from before and instantly frowned.

“Is everything alright?” he asked his tone changing from relaxed to worry.

“Yes it is, it was just a very stressful day.” You answered honestly and wiped them off your cheek.

First date:

For the first date he decided to take you out in your favorite restaurant. He already knew what your favorite restaurant is and he was very happy when he found out it was not one of that glamorous places where people wear fancy but uncomfortable clothes. The restaurant was very cozy and everything inside was designed to make people feel even better. When you two arrived the waiter showed you your table and when you sat down and chose your meals he left. Sam’s mood was like usual which means you were laughing most of the time. You noticed that he is a very nice guy and that you two have a lot of things in common. You two have a very good time together and at the end of your date you were already looking forward to your next meeting.

Relationship:

Your relationship is kind of that relationship in which one partner always teases the other one about the littlest things just to see them get fierce and pouty. In this case Sam always finds something to tease you about because he finds you adorable when you get angry and try to ignore him. He would then wrap arms around you and kiss your cheek couple of times until you start talking with him again. He knows how to fight and he is very good doing it so he is willing to teach you couple of moves and help you improve your skills. Sam may seem as very funny and sometimes serious person but he has a very sweet and gentle side whenever he is with you. He often kisses your hand, cheek and forehead and gives you weirdest but still the cutest nicknames and it’s one of his ways to show how much he loves you and how much you mean to him. He likes to listen to you while you sing or play the piano, he finds your voice beautiful and he has so many videos in his phone of you singing or playing the piano.

Nicknames:

Dearest, lady, bug…- He has so many nicknames for you and always keeps adding new ones on the list

Luv, ass- First one when he surprises you or when he is gentle and the second one when he teases you about something
